    {stage==="wheel"&&<><TDHost icon="🎡" title="转动幸运轮盘" text={`第 ${rounds+1} 轮 · ${settings.difficulty}模式`}/><div className={spinning?"td-wheel spinning":"td-wheel"}>{roster.map((p,i)=><span key={p.id} style={{transform:`rotate(${i*360/roster.length}deg) translateY(-105px) rotate(-${i*360/roster.length}deg)`}}>{p.avatar}</span>)}<b>🐾</b></div><div className="box-status-row">{roster.map(p=>{const pp=profile(p.name),active=Object.entries(pp.statuses||{}).filter(([,v])=>v&&v>0).length;return <div key={p.id}><b>{p.avatar} {p.name}</b><small>勇气 {pp.bravery} · 道具 {pp.items.length}/{capacityOf(pp)}{active?` · 状态 ${active}`:""}</small></div>})}</div><button className="primary td-main td-wheel-start" disabled={spinning} onClick={spin}>{spinning?"猫猫正在选…":"开始抽人"}</button></>}
    {stage==="choose"&&chosen&&<><TDHost icon={punishmentMode?"🔥":"🎉"} title={punishmentMode?`败者惩罚：${chosen.name}`:`幸运儿：${chosen.name}`} text={punishmentMode?`直接选择惩罚 · 后面还有 ${punishmentQueue.length} 位败者`:"可以先使用下方道具，再选择真心话或大冒险。"}/><div className="td-lucky"><span>{chosen.avatar}</span><b>{chosen.name}</b><small>{punishmentMode?`${punishmentLabel}指定惩罚 · 不发盲盒`:`${chosen.gender} · 接触偏好：${chosen.touchPreference}`}</small></div>{statusOf(profile(),"forceTruth")>0&&<p className="forced-mode-notice">👻 强制真心话生效中：本轮不能选择大冒险</p>}{statusOf(profile(),"forceDare")>0&&<p className="forced-mode-notice dare">🔥 强制大冒险生效中：本轮不能选择真心话</p>}{usableItems("choose")}{itemNotice&&<p className="item-notice">✨ {itemNotice}</p>}<div className="td-mode-cards"><button disabled={(!punishmentMode&&settings.mode==="大冒险")||statusOf(profile(),"forceDare")>0} onClick={()=>drawQuestion("真心话")}><span>❤️</span><b>真心话</b></button><button disabled={(!punishmentMode&&settings.mode==="真心话")||statusOf(profile(),"forceTruth")>0} onClick={()=>drawQuestion("大冒险")}><span>🔥</span><b>大冒险</b></button><button onClick={()=>drawQuestion("随机")}><span>🎲</span><b>随机</b></button></div></>}
